content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 78.28 - Vehicles to yield right-of-way to aircraft

State Regulations

All vehicles in or upon the airport, shall yield the right
of way to any and all aircraft in motion. However, emergency vehicles shall
have right-of-way over taxing aircraft. Notes
